cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.MM, cs.NE 

The paper deals with image reconstruction, specifically in the context of MRI. The use of active acquisition to reduce uncertainty in the reconstruction process suggests a focus on computer vision (cs.CV) and machine learning (cs.LG, cs.AI) techniques. The validation on a large scale dataset and the use of a ResNet-based architecture also suggest a focus on multimedia (cs.MM) and neural networks (cs.NE).
